Please join us as:

QA Manager

Quality Assurance Team

Job Description:

Design, implement, and improve company quality standards to achieve quality goals;
Conduct factory and outlets audits to identify any deviations from quality, hygiene and food safety standards;
Perform regular review of the manufacturing standard operating procedures (SOP) to ensure higher-quality goods and increase productivity;
Coordinate and follow through external audits by customers and third-party accreditation bodies;
Investigate customer complaints related to food quality.

Job Requirements:

Degree in Food science, Food safety or related disciplines;
Familiar with ISO22000 or ISO9000 and HACCP implementation;
5 years' relevant experience in QA management, with food industry experience would be an advantage;
Independent, fast-paced, multi-tasking, result-oriented and self-motivated.
Interested parties please apply with resume, current salary, expected salary and contact numbers to the Human Resources Manager, Tao Heung Group Ltd. by clicking "APPLY NOW".

Application letters collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.
